summary: An ordinance appropriating money from the General Fund to the State of Washington for the purpose of paying judgement with interest in favor of the State of Washington in the condemnation of Thirty-ninth Avenue North, instituted under Ordinance No. 42112; authorizing the drawing of a warrant therefor; providing for the repayment of said appropriation to the General Fund from the First moneys coming into the Local Improvement Condemnation Award District No. 3455.
